      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "FastAPI  (api/)\n─────────────────────\nProject CRUD\n  GET / POST  /projects\n  GET  /projects/{id}/status\n\nIngestion\n  POST /projects/{id}/documents\n  → background pipeline task\n\nRequirements\n  GET /projects/{id}/requirements\n      ?req_type= filter\n\nSDLC Docs  ← new\n  GET  /projects/{id}/docs\n  GET  /projects/{id}/docs/{topic}\n  POST /projects/{id}/docs/{topic}/edit\n\nClarifications\n  GET  /projects/{id}/clarifications\n  POST .../clarifications/{id}/answer\n\nRAG Search\n  POST /projects/{id}/query\n  → hybrid BM25 + Pinecone",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FastAPI  (api/)\n─────────────────────\nProject CRUD\n  GET / POST  /projects\n  GET  /projects/{id}/status\n\nIngestion\n  POST /projects/{id}/documents\n  → background pipeline task\n\nRequirements\n  GET /projects/{id}/requirements\n      ?req_type= filter\n\nSDLC Docs  ← new\n  GET  /projects/{id}/docs\n  GET  /projects/{id}/docs/{topic}\n  POST /projects/{id}/docs/{topic}/edit\n\nClarifications\n  GET  /projects/{id}/clarifications\n  POST .../clarifications/{id}/answer\n\nRAG Search\n  POST /projects/{id}/query\n  → hybrid BM25 + Pinecone",
